WEBVTT

00:01:55.167 --> 00:02:00.059
And it was, but what I found
is that we talked a lot.

00:02:00.083 --> 00:02:02.143
We talked about how we were feeling

00:02:02.167 --> 00:02:03.601
about the world,

00:02:03.625 --> 00:02:04.934
openly and honestly,

00:02:04.958 --> 00:02:08.309
and no one told me at any point
to be more positive

00:02:08.333 --> 00:02:09.583
or more hopeful.

00:02:10.542 --> 00:02:11.875
Not once.

00:02:12.875 --> 00:02:17.476
And surprisingly,
I found myself feeling better.

00:02:17.500 --> 00:02:19.976
I actually felt like
I could face these issues

00:02:20.000 --> 00:02:22.851
that had seemed so insurmountable

00:02:22.875 --> 00:02:25.059
more head on.

00:02:25.083 --> 00:02:27.143
And I had this epiphany:

00:02:27.167 --> 00:02:30.143
What if by understanding ourselves